Package: SFDesign
Type: Package
Title: Space-Filling Designs
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-04-25
Authors@R: c(person("Shangkun", "Wang",, "shangkunwang01@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Roshan", "Joseph",,"roshan@gatech.edu", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: Shangkun Wang <shangkunwang01@gmail.com>
Description: Construct various types of space-filling designs, including Latin hypercube designs, clustering-based designs, maximin designs, maximum projection designs, and uniform designs (Joseph 2016 <doi:10.1080/08982112.2015.1100447>). It also offers the option to optimize designs based on user-defined criteria.
Depends: Rcpp (>= 1.0.8)
Imports: GenSA, nloptr, primes, proxy, spacefillr
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Repository: CRAN
NeedsCompilation: yes
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
